14
00:00:18,109 --> 00:00:19,563
Marry me, Cristina Yang.

15
00:00:19,715 --> 00:00:20,463
Marry me.

16
00:00:22,977 --> 00:00:27,330
As surgeons, we live in a world
of worst-case scenarios.

17
00:00:27,908 --> 00:00:30,371
We cut ourselves off
from hoping for the best

18
00:00:30,528 --> 00:00:33,881
because too many times,
the best doesn't happen.

19
00:00:34,965 --> 00:00:38,930
But every now and then,
something extraordinary occurs...

20
00:01:02,548 --> 00:01:04,750
and suddenly...

21
00:01:05,095 --> 00:01:08,263
best-case scenarios seem possible.

22
00:01:08,326 --> 00:01:12,860
- 8 days, $8 million...
- and we're open for business.

23
00:01:13,048 --> 00:01:17,162
And every now and then,
something amazing happens...

24
