She woke up this morning
completely aware.

25
00:01:20,367 --> 00:01:22,060
She's her old self. It happens.

26
00:01:22,165 --> 00:01:25,120
Medically, we don't know why.
It's just a random gift.

27
00:01:25,246 --> 00:01:26,692
So she's lucid? She remembers?

28
00:01:26,736 --> 00:01:27,562
Pretty much everything,

29
00:01:27,686 --> 00:01:30,993
except the last five years. And, of course,
she doesn't realize she has Alzheimer's.

30
00:01:31,166 --> 00:01:32,951
