52
00:02:21,548 --> 00:02:22,272
Well, you should.

53
00:02:24,857 --> 00:02:27,233
I was, uh, heading down to the clinic.

54
00:02:27,638 --> 00:02:28,972
It's opening today, and I

55
00:02:29,577 --> 00:02:32,071
