Mom! Somebody call 9-1-1.

94
00:03:51,777 --> 00:03:53,661
- She had substernal chest...
- Chest pain and syncope.

95
00:03:53,727 --> 00:03:56,780
My pulse was in the 200s, but the
rate has resolved on its own.

96
00:03:57,555 --> 00:03:58,651
She's completely lucid.

97
00:03:59,078 --> 00:03:59,570
