98
00:04:00,555 --> 00:04:01,290
She's aware.

99
00:04:01,357 --> 00:04:02,403
She's herself again.

100
00:04:02,638 --> 00:04:03,921
Oh, my god. Is this...

101
00:04:04,368 --> 00:04:05,541
