102
00:04:05,576 --> 00:04:07,492
Yes, mom. This is where
I'm doing my residency.

103
00:04:07,507 --> 00:04:09,553
Your daughter is one of
our finest interns,

104
00:04:09,587 --> 00:04:11,880
