the protocol for the flu vaccine.

115
00:04:34,895 --> 00:04:37,111
Oh, no, no, no. Don't... don't...
don't touch that.

116
00:04:37,185 --> 00:04:39,240
That was $79.

117
00:04:40,716 --> 00:04:41,660
Oh, my god.

118
00:04:41,697 --> 00:04:43,571
