00:04:46,376 --> 00:04:47,792
fly in from Denver tomorrow.

121
00:04:47,836 --> 00:04:48,832
I should be preparing.

122
00:04:48,888 --> 00:04:50,861
You don't get to scrub in
on the valve translocation.

123
00:04:50,876 --> 00:04:51,751
How do you know?

124
00:04:51,807 --> 00:04:52,312
Because I am.

125
00:04:53,317 --> 00:04:54,091
