Denny's money can do, right?

138
00:05:16,517 --> 00:05:17,941
Just watch the doors, Stevens.

139
00:05:29,408 --> 00:05:30,220
Dr. Bailey,

140
00:05:30,518 --> 00:05:32,902
congratulations on the
opening of the clinic.

141
00:05:32,957 --> 00:05:34,621
It is open, isn't it?

142
00:05:38,147 --> 00:05:39,801
