157
00:06:39,075 --> 00:06:39,841
Yay.

158
00:06:40,575 --> 00:06:41,641
Show her the ring.

159
00:06:41,677 --> 00:06:41,933
Oh.

160
00:06:42,787 --> 00:06:43,961
Oh.

161
00:06:44,107 --> 00:06:45,351
