175
00:07:12,057 --> 00:07:12,730
We're married.

176
00:07:14,557 --> 00:07:15,933
We're married.

177
00:07:17,597 --> 00:07:18,033
All right.

178
00:07:21,216 --> 00:07:21,942
So, chief,

179
00:07:22,316 --> 00:07:23,692
