that was Adele's idea.

218
00:08:39,957 --> 00:08:40,192
Meredith.

219
00:08:40,915 --> 00:08:42,053
I'll be right there, mom.

220
00:08:42,326 --> 00:08:42,712
Go ahead.

221
00:08:47,995 --> 00:08:49,071
She's lucid.

222
00:08:49,737 --> 00:08:52,061
