255
00:10:13,476 --> 00:10:14,411
Almost an hour.

256
00:10:14,436 --> 00:10:14,880
Mm.

257
00:10:14,986 --> 00:10:15,473
Mm.

258
00:10:16,036 --> 00:10:16,743
